<div style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; caret-color: #000000;" data-page-id="QjAIdBPc9onYt6x59cWlV80Zgs6" data-lark-html-role="root" data-docx-has-block-data="false">
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ObCBd6q0ZoHV8hxF6GrltbsvgFf">🌟Eligibility &amp; Participation</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SIdBdyv2BogSMsxmXbHlNgWvgmb">1.This campaign will run from July 17, 2026, to July 20, 2026 (UTC), and is open to all new and existing LBank users.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-CGU5dkMAqopufJxDk3ql9TK9gke">2.Users must click “Register Now” to enroll.Each user may participate with one account only. Multiple or duplicate accounts will be disqualified.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LiO1d7X5WoVXSfxA2N5lO8KLgfb">3.This campaign cannot be combined with the Newcomer Benefits Center.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BreGdvwNgo2Y2jx27oBl7ucpgcf">🌟 Bonuses &amp; Rewards</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-J9dwddjXfol7yXx4tM8l3ibqgvc">【Welcome Bonus】</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JcNqdZWuGoFYyhxi4Xcll0s6got">1.Users must complete registration.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-M4AAdUOfToHppcx7MV5l1ojvgWe">2.Deposit ≥ 100 USDT (or equivalent) via on-chain transfer; internal transfers excluded.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BLrFdpgHRoMUmwxn2w0l3f9NgTc">3.Keep funds in your account for 3 days; withdrawals void the reward.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WmepdY6AHoVs3qxvROelLhwigbg">【Trading Task Rewards】</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-L0rRdZwyuoS2QkxRk4xlufTrghc">1.For both spot trading and futures trading, the trading volume of tokens from any trading pair will be counted.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-UD4gdj9zso9Z3qxZGqLlBqXfgJg">2.Trading volume is calculated as total buy + sell volume during the campaign period.Trading volume generated using futures bonus is not included.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-JdyndiOouosfYsxbRa9l7ToTgcf">3.The futures bonus is claimable only after the futures account balance reaches ≥ 10 USDT.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-A0gad6ohwodGycxI91hl172sgTc">4.Bonus validity: 7 days after issuance.&nbsp;</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K4tgdTAYpoMnJexZK0IlTG9pg3d">🌟Futures Bonus Rules</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BZugd9ttWocirIxNUsSlQ7sdgLh">1.Futures bonus is for trading only and cannot be withdrawn or transferred.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SCDDdb61JocxPaxsb6wlMdNygsc">2.Validity: 3 days (welcome bonus), 7 days (task rewards)</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-TSQHdY6rooB4XNxp2hclSynTg2f">3..Profits generated may be withdrawn (subject to platform rules) Bonus-generated trading volume does not count toward tasks</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-SnZldGphxomMn5xRnVvlZTsKgSe">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-BOjJdgNCkocO9yxMC1IlU41bglg">🌟Risk &amp; Compliance</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-DLZmdlck8otryzxGLgHlapMYgtd">1.Users flagged as abnormal or engaging in fraudulent behavior will be disqualified and rewards canceled.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-FlgZdunO0o8y7MxfL20lTpp0gef">2.LBank reserves the right to modify the campaign terms and retains final interpretation rights.</div>
<div class="ace-line ace-line old-record-id-K2j2d8FwKoH2A7xV6RPlHE0Igzh">3.Users from Bangladesh, India and Pakistan are not eligible to participate.</div>
</div>